libplacebo provides pkg-config metadata:

    find_package(PkgConfig REQUIRED)
    pkg_check_modules(LIBPLACEBO REQUIRED IMPORTED_TARGET libplacebo)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE PkgConfig::LIBPLACEBO)

This port enables the Vulkan renderer, shaderc, and libplacebo's built-in
Dolby Vision reshaping support on Windows and Linux.
